	.string "完美搞定！\p"
	.string "{STR_VAR_1}已经将\n"
	.string "{STR_VAR_2}忘得一干二净了。$"

FuchsiaCity_House3_Text_ComeAgainToForgetOtherMoves::
	.string "如果你有别的技能想要忘记\n"
	.string "那么欢迎再次光临。$"

FuchsiaCity_House3_Text_NoEggShouldKnowMoves::
	.string "你在想什么？\n"
	.string "蛋怎么可能会学技能。$"

